            "text": "Such an ordering provides an easier path to learning ",
            "relation": "CAUSE-RESULT-REASON"
        },
        {
            "id": 4,
            "parent": 3,
            "text": "and increases the speed of acquisition of the task ",
            "relation": "JOINT"
        },
        {
            "id": 5,
            "parent": 4,
            "text": "compared to conventional learning . <S>",
            "relation": "COMPARISON"
        },
        {
            "id": 6,
            "parent": 11,
            "text": "Recent works in machine learning have explored a curriculum learning approach ",
            "relation": "BACKGROUND"
        },
        {
            "id": 7,
            "parent": 6,
            "text": "called selfpaced learning ",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 8,
            "parent": 7,
            "text": "which orders data samples on the easiness scale ",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 9,
            "parent": 8,
            "text": "so that easy samples can be introduced to the learning algorithm first ",
            "relation": "ENABLEMENT"
        },
        {
            "id": 10,
            "parent": 9,
            "text": "and harder samples can be introduced successively . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 11,
            "parent": 0,
            "text": "We introduce a number of heuristics ",
            "relation": "ROOT"
        },
        {
            "id": 12,
