            "text": "that improve upon selfpaced learning . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 13,
            "parent": 14,
            "text": "Then , we argue ",
            "relation": "ATTRIBUTION"
        },
        {
            "id": 14,
            "parent": 11,
            "text": "that incorporating easy , yet , a diverse set of samples can further improve learning . <S>",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
        },
        {
            "id": 15,
            "parent": 17,
            "text": "We compare these curriculum learning proposals in the context of four non-convex models for QA ",
            "relation": "ELABORATION"
